From sjaffe at riskspan.com  Tue Jul 23 18:50:04 2013
From: sjaffe at riskspan.com (Steve Jaffe)
Date: Tue, 23 Jul 2013 11:50:04 -0500
Subject: [Rcpp-devel] Rcpp-devel] What is the best practice to expose a
 C structure from 3rd party library into R?
Message-ID: <C03F8157B6DECC428DE8D36DC5F9244114F1308EAF@DFW1MBX03.mex07a.mlsrvr.com>

